repository.name: Haalsamachar-app
repository.description: Application Repository for HaalSamachar consisting of Backend Microservices built with GoLang including a GraphQL API built using gqlgen and four REST APIs built using Gin and frontend built with NextJs+TypeScript with PostgreSQL powered database, containerized using Docker.
